latestIgtvVideos.title: Taro Arai Makes Kuze Fuku & Sons Roll
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We've teamed up with Tari Arai (@mikunitaro), the Chief Dreaming Officer of Mikuni Sushi (@mikunisushi), to make the sushi roll of our dreams: The Kuze Fuku & Sons Roll.  🍣
Through this recipe, Chef Taro has found the perfect way to combine the rich and savory taste of our Traditional Umami Dashi, with the citrusy and delicate notes of our Yuzu Miso Premium Sauce.
Find these products in select Costco locations, as well as on our website.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Kuze Fuku & Sons Introduction
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Introducing Kuze Fuku & Sons, maker of authentic, simple and pure food and beverages created by Japanese gourmet craftsmen for your enjoyment. Kuze Fuku & Sons selections include authentic Japanese items and other delicious choices inspired by the food culture of Portland, Oregon. Utilizing a wide variety of locally sourced ingredients, our products include dashi, fruit vinegars, sauces, jams, and more. Visit kuzefukuandsons.com for more details!
